<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>13298</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17193</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁的妈妈吓呆了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17194</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20638</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首席大臣向她走去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20639</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>25243</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他抓住泽巴的胳膊，把她拉向国王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>25244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29414</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“过来，女人！”他不耐烦地说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35769</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴跌跌撞撞地向国王走去，跪在他的面前。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35770</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>45037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，国王。”她喊道，“祝愿您幸福长久地统治国家！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>45038</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49907</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请站起来，善良的女人。”苏丹王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49908</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55433</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我每天都看见你，但是你从来不说话。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55434</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59882</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>现在请告诉我你来这里的目的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59883</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>69509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，国王！”她请求道，“在您答应我一件事情之前我什么都不能说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>69510</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>75318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您必须答应免我和我儿子一死！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>75319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>82729</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王听到这些话之后惊讶极了，他看了看旁边的大臣。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>82730</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86094</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>首席大臣耸了耸肩。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86095</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>92401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“好吧，善良的女人，我保证不杀你。”国王说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>92402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>97636</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“也不能杀我的儿子。”泽巴补充道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>97637</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104903</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不杀你的儿子！”国王大笑着说，“现在请说吧！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104904</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>113703</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后泽巴把阿拉丁躲在门后偷看贝德拉公主的事情告诉了国王。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>113704</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>118450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他没有遵守我的命令？”国王皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>118451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>121614</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴做了一个深呼吸。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>121615</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>125793</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“是的，他没遵守。”她难过地说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>125794</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我儿子看见了她的脸。他觉得她是最美的女孩儿。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132232</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>136082</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王又皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>136083</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>145835</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在他说如果他不能和你女儿结婚，他会死的！”泽巴屏住呼吸说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>145836</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156100</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王怒眼瞪着泽巴，整个大厅都屏住呼吸，等国王说什么或做什么。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156101</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>164226</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哈哈……”国王突然大笑，“你有个疯狂的儿子，女人！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>164227</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大厅里的每个人都跟着苏丹王笑了起来，泽巴松了一口气。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>179388</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后她把碗举到苏丹王面前，把盖着珠宝的布拿开。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>179389</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185732</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这是我儿子阿拉丁给您的礼物！”她大声说道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185733</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>191400</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人看到那些闪亮的宝石之后都惊叹不已。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>191401</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198692</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>当国王看到碗里闪闪发光的珠宝时，他停止了笑容。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198693</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208194</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王有金山银山，但是他从没见过这么美的珠宝！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208195</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215719</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我宫殿里最大的宝石都比这里面最小的宝石还小！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215720</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220912</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王惊叫着，拿起了一块大红宝石。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220913</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225087</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“首席大臣，你见过这样的珠宝吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225088</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231561</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“没有，陛下，从来没见过。”大臣闷闷不乐地回答道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231562</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>237238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“送给我这礼物的人应该成为我的女婿！”国王说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>237239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你不赞成吗，首席大臣？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是，陛下！”首席大臣大吃了一惊说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245580</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>251826</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“您难道忘记了吗？您早已经答应把公主嫁给我儿子了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>251827</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>258237</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王看着地板，说道：“你说得对，我的朋友，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>258238</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263038</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是这个礼物改变了所有的事情。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263039</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268250</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我的女儿要嫁给这个王国里最富有的人。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268251</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273652</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“国王，”首席大臣说，“请别急着下定论。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273653</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>278774</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>您对这个叫阿拉丁的年轻人一点儿都不了解。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>278775</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>283401</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>国王忽略了他的请求，转向泽巴。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>283402</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>288205</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“去告诉你儿子，我会把女儿嫁给他的，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>288206</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>297008</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是我需要三个月的时间准备这场盛大的婚礼。告诉他要有耐心。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>297009</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301798</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>泽巴谢了国王，高兴地回家了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301799</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>307155</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁一直看着窗户，等待着他的母亲。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>307156</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313816</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>终于，他看见他的母亲从弯弯曲曲的道路尽头跑回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>313817</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>320064</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她的头巾在身后飞扬，但是她一边跑一边微笑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>320065</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328529</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>阿拉丁注意到了更重要的事情 — 泽巴手上没有了那个装满珠宝的碗。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328530</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336346</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“国王已经接受了我的礼物！”他高兴地大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>